snippet.title: Saleblazers Early Access Launch Trailer (Sept. 29th)
snippet.description:
Wishlist Saleblazers on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1419850/Saleblazers/

0:18 - Skip to gameplay footage

Saleblazers is a multiplayer shopkeeping survival game coming soon to Steam on September 29th! We hope you'll have lots of fun.

Join our Discord to give us feedback: https://discord.gg/Saleblazers
